            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-dhlHIi fuaxyy\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Lam Research <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"LRCX\" style=\"display:inline-block\">LRCX</span> has outperformed the market over the past 5 years by 5.88% on an annualized basis producing an average annual return of 19.76%. Currently, Lam Research has a market capitalization of $121.29 billion. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Buying $1000 In LRCX:</strong> If an investor had bought $1000 of LRCX stock 5 years ago, it would be worth <strong>$2,486.56</strong> today based on a price of $94.82 for LRCX at the time of writing.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-dGJnDi cqLODL\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold\">Trending Investment Opportunities</div><div class=\"flex items-end justify-end\"><div class=\"text-right text-sm bg-gray-200 rounded px-2 py-1\">Advertisement</div></div></div></div><div class=\"cta-stacked GalleryCarousel_splide_slidewrap__zHpTC\"><div class=\"sc-cwcSVF hlcLHF carousel-container\"><div aria-label=\"Carousel\" class=\"splide\"><div class=\"splide-track-wrapper\"><div class=\"splide__track\"><ul class=\"splide__list\"><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"carousel-pagination\"><div class=\"splide__arrows\"><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev page-left-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1